{"tid":1193323,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【6.9 大遊行】獨派組織籲支持者遊行後「不散」　將宣佈「重要事項」","createTime":"2019-06-09T00:23:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-09T00:59:22.000Z","uid":254183,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e945503692bfdcb698c8123bd544251cdc4654eb","tid":1193323,"uid":254183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T00:23:21.000Z","msg":"民間人權陣線發起的「反送中」、要求撤回逃犯條例修訂的大遊行，今天（6 月 9 日）下午舉行，估計會有數十萬人參與，有可能是 2003 年後香港最大規模的遊行，民陣強調是一次和平行動，對於之後會否有升級行動認為言之尚早。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">但多個支持港獨的獨派組織在社交媒體發佈消息，呼籲支持者在遊行後不要解散，並將有重要事項宣佈</span></strong>。作出同類呼籲的獨派組織包括學生動源、香港民族陣綫、香港獨立聯盟等。<br />\n<br />\n《香港01》引述學生動源的鍾翰林表示，明日遊行時，會否發起更激烈的抗爭，要視乎情況，最主要考慮是警方採用武力的程度，他強調，該組織的宗旨是「抗爭無底線」，明日會盡量維持和平、非暴力的抗爭模式，但不排除因應警方的行動，調整抗爭模式。他又透露，該組織會盡量與同屬港獨派的香港獨立聯盟一同行動，而他亦曾與部分泛民主派組織溝通，「大家互相知道對方會發起的行動」，共識是盡量不干預、不影響對方。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s0cx3hk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs0cx3hk.png&h=4b876c53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/6-9-%E5%A4%A7%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C-%E7%8D%A8%E6%B4%BE%E7%B5%84%E7%B9%94%E7%B1%B2%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E8%80%85%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C%E5%BE%8C-%E4%B8%8D%E6%95%A3-%E5%B0%87%E5%AE%A3%E4%BD%88-%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%E4%BA%8B%E9%A0%85/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F6-9-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C-%25E7%258D%25A8%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E7%25B5%2584%25E7%25B9%2594%25E7%25B1%25B2%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258C%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C%25E5%25BE%258C-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2595%25A3-%25E5%25B0%2587%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E4%25BD%2588-%25E9%2587%258D%25E8%25A6%2581%25E4%25BA%258B%25E9%25A0%2585%2F&d=%2BD6XGwqev%2FlZKpArKwvoHVYPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=07df9a67\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F6-9-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C-%25E7%258D%25A8%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E7%25B5%2584%25E7%25B9%2594%25E7%25B1%25B2%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258C%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C%25E5%25BE%258C-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2595%25A3-%25E5%25B0%2587%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E4%25BD%2588-%25E9%2587%258D%25E8%25A6%2581%25E4%25BA%258B%25E9%25A0%2585%2F&h=f0744ba2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/6-9-%E5%A4%A7%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C-%E7%8D%A8%E6%B4%BE%E7%B5%84%E7%B9%94%E7%B1%B2%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E8%80%85%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C%E5%BE%8C-%E4%B8%8D%E6%95%A3-%E5%B0%87%E5%AE%A3%E4%BD%88-%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%E4%BA%8B%E9%A0%85/</a>"},{"pid":"e1384d8b12857d21fad91990bde1f679b80eda68","tid":1193323,"uid":254183,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T00:47:08.000Z","msg":"不散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5385fadcd1e86fbc9bc015b291840d24df03682","tid":1193323,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1384d8b12857d21fad91990bde1f679b80eda68","tid":1193323,"uid":254183,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T00:47:08.000Z","msg":"不散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T00:59:22.000Z","msg":"6月9號遊行嘅方針:兄弟爬山，各自努力，避免割席，拒絕篤灰，不打飛機，不傳耳語，不搞抹黑<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1192414\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1192414</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}